   This program control the package routing by binding host route dynamiclly. The brt-server is the abbreviation of
 bind route server .

1).Compile the program.
   make
   
   Note:If you use tftp,please modify the TFTP_BOOT_DIR as your environment.
2) Insall
   Please add the following code to /etc/rc.local.
   /usr/app/brt-bump.sh & 
  
   Please copy brt-server to /usr/app directory and make it excutable.


  Note: The path of application and script will be changed in the future. Now it only be used for testing.

 	
